front.title: •Accepting Trade Federation Control
front.gametext: Deploy on table. If no senator here, you may place a senator here from hand to subtract 3 from any battle destiny just drawn. If a taxation agenda here, your draw phase, you may activate 1 Force; opponent must use 1 Force (if possible).
front.lore: Palpatine suggested to the Queen that she acquiesce to the Trade Federation, just for the time being
